                <note rend="inline" type="source">125.1333/326: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Consul General at Algiers (<persName type="from"
                            >Cole</persName>) to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Algiers</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1942-11-09">November 9,
                            1942</date>.<lb/>[Received December 5—7:41 a.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>3. Entire staff of Consulate General at Algiers safe and well. Individual
                    inquiries indicate all American residents of whom Consulate General has record
                    also safe and well.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Cole</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
